data.description: USE SELLER'S ALLOWANCE TO REDUCE YOUR MONTHLY PAYMENT!  Welcome to your dream home in Bridgewood! This stunning property has undergone a complete transformation, both inside and out, ensuring a modern and luxurious living experience. Step inside to discover a harmonious blend of comfort and style with fresh paint, updated light fixtures, and water-resistant laminate flooring that extends seamlessly throughout the home.  The heart of this residence is the gourmet kitchen, a culinary enthusiast's delight. Revel in the elegance of white tiled backsplash, stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and an abundance of handsome cabinetry that provides both style and functionality. The convenient breakfast bar opens to an adjoining dining area, offering the perfect space to enjoy meals while overlooking the backyard oasis. Privacy is key, with a brand-new fence ensuring seclusion and no immediate neighbors in the rear.  Your primary suite is a true retreat, boasting ample space for a private sitting area, creating a haven within your home. The two fully renovated bathrooms exude sophistication with new plumbing fixtures, lights, quartz vanities, and meticulously tiled showers.  The spacious and flexible floor plan is designed to cater to your lifestyle, providing multiple living and dining areas, each offering generous storage space with walk-in closets. Whether you're hosting a gathering or seeking moments of tranquility, this home effortlessly accommodates your needs.  Enjoy peace of mind with additional features, including a new roof and a foundation expertly repaired with a lifetime warranty. Convenience is at your fingertips with easy access to Loop 1604, I-10, and Highway 151, making commuting a breeze.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this meticulously renovated and strategically located home yours. Welcome to a lifestyle of comfort, elegance, and convenience in Bridgewood!
